author: By LINDSAY WHITEHURST Associated Press
title: Summit County issues stay-home order to handle coronavirus
description: SALT LAKE CITY (AP) — A Utah county hard hit by the new coronavirus is telling residents to stay home except for essential errands and asking visitors to the ski-resort community of Park City to stay away.
